WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
The micro:bit shows a sad face.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Button A on the micro:bit is pressed.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:10.000
The micro:bit shows a paper.

00:00:10.00 --> 00:00:13.000
The micro:bit shows a smiling face.

00:00:13.00 --> 00:00:17.000
Press the micro:bit logo.

00:00:17.00 --> 00:00:25.000
The micro:bit shows a scissors.

00:00:25.00 --> 00:00:28.000
The micro:bit shows a smiling face.